  "texts": [
    "One of the most compelling prospects offered by AI in education is the personalization of learning experiences.",
    "AI's capacity to tailor educational content to the unique learning styles and needs of each student holds the potential for a more engaging and effective educational journey.",
    "Moreover, this technology has shown remarkable promise in supporting students with special needs, thereby enhancing inclusivity and accessibility in learning environments.",
    "Additionally, the focus on AI literacy, prompt engineering, and critical thinking skills prepares students for the complexities of a technology-driven world, equipping them with essential competencies for the future.",
    "However, these advancements bring forth their own set of challenges."
  ],
